Adnexor: Positive Impact Ads or nothing. 

This extension allows users to receive only positive impact ads. 

With Adnexor, you can contribute to having a positive impact on society simply by browsing the web, for free and effortless. Download Adnexor now and start making the difference! 

By empowering our users, they regain control of their attention, which everyone on the web is constantly trying to capture. This way, anyone who wants to reach Adnexor's users must connect with positive impact. 

Our mission is to help homeless people find a home and Adnexor is a tool that allows you to actively participate in achieving this goal.
